ains on the skull it wears are from its tears."},{"version":"firered","text":"It wears the skull of its dead mother on its head. When it becomes lonesome, it is said to cry loudly."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Because it never removes its skull helmet, no one has ever seen this POK\u00e9MON\u2019s real face."},{"version":"diamond","text":"When it thinks of its dead mother, it cries. Its crying makes the skull it wears rattle hollowly."},{"version":"pearl","text":"When it thinks of its dead mother, it cries. Its crying makes the skull it wears rattle hollowly."},{"version":"platinum","text":"When it thinks of its dead mother, it cries. Its crying makes the skull it wears rattle hollowly."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"If it is sad or lonely, the skull it wears shakes and emits a plaintive and mournful sound."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"It always wears the skull of its dead mother, so no one has any idea what its hidden face looks like."},{"version":"black","text":"When it thinks of its dead mother, it cries. Its crying makes the skull it wears rattle hollowly."},{"version":"white","text":"When it thinks of its dead mother, it cries. Its crying makes the skull it wears rattle hollowly."},{"version":"black-2","text":"When it thinks of its dead mother, it cries. Its crying makes the skull it wears rattle hollowly."},{"version":"white-2","text":"When it thinks of its dead mother, it cries. Its crying makes the skull it wears rattle hollowly."},{"version":"x","text":"It wears the skull of its dead mother on its head. When it becomes lonesome, it is said to cry loudly."},{"version":"y","text":"It always wears the skull of its dead mother, so no one has any idea what its hidden face looks like."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Cubone pines for the mother it will never see again. Seeing a likeness of its mother in the full moon, it cries. The stains on the skull the Pok\u00e9mon wears are made by the tears it sheds."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Cubone pines for the mother it will never see again. Seeing a likeness of its mother in the full moon, it cries. The stains on the skull the Pok\u00e9mon wears are made by the tears it sheds."},{"version":"sun","text":"When it thinks of its deceased mother, it weeps loudly. Mandibuzz that hear its cries will attack it from the air."},{"version":"moon","text":"The skull it wears on its head is that of its dead mother. According to some, it will evolve when it comes to terms with the pain of her death."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"At night, it weeps loudly for its dead mother, but those cries only attract its natural enemy\u2014Mandibuzz."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"It wears its mother\u2019s skull on its head, so no one knows what its bare face looks like. However, it\u2019s clear that it\u2019s always crying."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Wears the skull of its deceased mother. Its cries echo inside the skull and come out as a sad melody."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Wears the skull of its deceased mother. Its cries echo inside the skull and come out as a sad melody."},{"version":"sword","text":"When the memory of its departed mother brings it to tears, its cries echo mournfully within the skull it wears on its head."},{"version":"shield","text":"This Pok\u00e9mon wears the skull of its deceased mother. Sometimes Cubone\u2019s dreams make it cry, but each tear Cubone sheds makes it stronger."}],"evo":{"name":"cubone","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"marowak","level":1,"min_level":28,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_ups